&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are seeking an experienced, self starting, (US - North East based) Account Executive to join our highly ambitious Commercial team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will have a focus on identifying and generating opportunities with market leaders within the logistics industry to showcase our transformational technology. You will be responsible for ensuring the growth of our pipeline, keeping a keen eye out for opportunities and solution evangelism while helping with continuous improvement of the sales cycle.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Taking a team- based approach to consultative selling, you’ll partner with our Commercial Implementation/Solutions, Product and Marketing teams to ensure a world class end-to-end client experience.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you are looking for a role with a commission up to 100%, this is the role for you!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;To be successful in this role you will:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage &amp;amp; lead the full sales lifecycle, start to finish to meet and exceed quarterly targets and sales quotas&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Learn, support and find solutions for clients and will consultatively show how Dexory can bring real value in their long term gains&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Target and build long term relationships with C-Suite - level stakeholders&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work with our VP Business Development to strategise and carry out short/long term onboarding and growth plans for new clients and&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Working across the whole sales/commercials function during the sales process to ensure each prospect has the appropriate amount of assistance from a technical and functional perspective&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
