&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Minimum of 1 year&#39;s with B2B mid market to enterprise sales . SaaS and logistics experience are strongly preferred.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Constantly meeting/exceeding your individual sales quota&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with establishing relationships with and selling through technology partners and system integrators within the logistics &amp;amp; retail sector&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in large commercial negotiations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
