&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work with innovative robotics technology and real-world autonomous systems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Gain hands-on experience across software, hardware, and testing disciplines&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with experienced engineers in a supportive environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop valuable industry skills in robotics validation and quality engineering&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Be part of a team building the next generation of intelligent robotic platforms&lt;/li&gt;
